Preparation
• Stretch before starting this challenge.
• Find a suitable space for this exercise before pressing START.
• You’ll have a 4-second countdown after pressing START to prepare.
During the Challenge
• Aim for at least 10 repetitions or more.
• Complete as many reps as you can within 30 seconds.
• If time runs out, you’ll be redirected back to the homepage.
Finishing the Challenge
• When done, enter the number of reps you completed in the REPS field, then press DONE.
Exercise Guide
• Start in a plank position and hands shoulder-width apart.
• Lower your body and Bring your chest close to the floor, then push back up.
• Maintain form and keep your body straight and engage your core.
Note
Be honest with your exercise. This challenge is here to help you grow stronger so put in your best effort!
"Strength doesn’t come from what you can do. It comes from overcoming the things you once thought you couldn’t."
